snippet.title: EA Sports MMA Gameplay (HD)
snippet.description:
CHEK OUT MY NEW "FIFA 11 MONTAGE" :) http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ny6FAQal6S8 


Some gameplay of the brand new EA Sports game MMA for Xbox 360. This is the demo version of the game.
This video is a test of my new Hauppauge HD PVR to see what the quality would look like on youtube.

This is a match between Bobby Lashley and Alistair Overeem.

Sweet Knock-Out at the end !!! :P

Enjoy and comment on the quality of the video.

A.R
